metadata.name: GANyonlands National Park
metadata.description:
I have always loved this place since visiting for vacation as a young boy. I grew up in Northern Utah and we do have rocks like this around, but not so many concentrated in one place with the isolation from the cities and the sounds of civilization.

Tools used:

Visual. Camera. Adobe Fresco. Photoshop. After Effects. Disco Diffusion. StyleGAN

Audio. Gibson SG. Blackstar Dept 10 Dual Drive. Fender Rumble 100. FlStudio
